# Test Cases – Send Location

## Description
Tests the ability to share the user’s current or nearby location with a contact via the "+" attachment menu in a chat.

## Platforms Covered
- Android
- iOS
- Web *(only live location sending is not available)*
- Desktop *(location sharing not supported on all desktop platforms)*

## Preconditions
- User is logged in and inside a chat window.
- Location services/GPS are enabled on the device.
- Necessary location permissions are granted.

